			<div class="faqs-right-content">
				<div class="faqs-question">
					<h4>How do I make yoggie?</h4>
				</div>
				<div class="faqs-answer">
					<p>Empty entire yoggie pack into blender (straight from freezer). Add about 200ml (this varies) of water (or milk or soya or almond milk or yoghurt or juice - whatever you like!). Blend.</p>
				</div>
			</div>
