			<div class="faqs-right-content">
				<div class="faqs-question">
					<h4>What blender do you recommend?</h4>
				</div>
				<div class="faqs-answer">
					<p>We’ve burned out lots of blenders in our quest for the Ultimate Smoothie!<br>
					For most people we recommend at least a 1000 watt NutriBullet or equivalent with a min 750ml cup.<br>
					Serious smoothie blitzers and those on larger (>400kcal) custom yoggies should look at more substantial ones with  over 1 litre cups (such as Vitamix S30).</p>
				</div>
			</div>
			<div class="faqs-right-content">
				<div class="faqs-question">
					<h4>Fridge or freezer?</h4>
				</div>
				<div class="faqs-answer">
					<p>Store your yoggie packs in the freezer. They taste best blended straight from frozen. If you have to store them in the fridge they’ll be OK for up to 24 hours.<br>
					TIP: the ingredients will be pretty mushy when you empty into blender - try blending with a few ice cubes to get ice cold!</p>
				</div>
