					<h4>How long will my Yoggie last after I blend it? </h4>
				</div>
				<div class="faqs-answer">
					<p>If you don’t drink immediately just put in fridge or thermos flask/bottle and it’ll be good for around 6 hours. The layers will separate but that’s completely normal. Give it a good shake and you’re good to go.<br>
